Agent primitives are managed via [APM](https://github.com/microsoft/apm).

```
apm install          # install agent dependencies + generate context
apm add <dep>        # add a new dependency
apm run <script>     # invoke a named script
```

Author custom [instructions](https://microsoft.github.io/apm/producer/author-primitives/), [skills](https://microsoft.github.io/apm/producer/author-primitives/skills/), and [prompts](https://microsoft.github.io/apm/producer/author-primitives/prompts/) under `.apm/`.
